        "text": "HECKLER (B) must remain in his circle at all times while his team is defensive. He may at-\ntempt to stop the flight of the SAUCER, or distract the Filer in any manner. Should he step\nor fall out of his circle, his team forfeits 1 point and the offensive team retains serve."
